skins.selfIntroduction: I'm Niizuki, I'm the fifth ship of the Akizuki-class, I was constructed as part of the Circle Four Plan. But... I might be the least useful ship ever constructed... *Sob*...
skins.acquisition: I'm Niizuki, the fifth ship of the Akizuki-class. I-I sincerely hope I can be of servish to... *Whimper*... I've made another mistake... Even though I practiced on it so much...
skins.login: Commander, I've sorted all your documents... You wanted your documents sorted... right?
skins.details: C-Commander, I haven't, um... disappointed you... have I?
skins.secretaryIdle1: I want to be useful to you, Commander, but if I cause you trouble instead... Then what will I do...
skins.secretaryIdle2: If I cause you any trouble, I'll let you touch my ears and my tail, so please don't get mad at me...
skins.secretaryIdle3: For this one you do this, then here you do... this... I think? I-I hope this will work...
skins.secretaryTouch: Commander? I'm worrying if I did something wrong today... I-I don't think... I have...
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: Eek?! C-Commander... you're seriously going to make me cry...
